product__description: Tempting with a pop of bright color, the Amelie Shamrock Couture lamp adds a resonating impact to a bedroom or living space. Embrace this table lamp made of ceramic and coated with an Irish green finish, highlighting its jar silhouette. A warm gold leaf finished base and cream box pleated silk shade creates a tasteful aesthetic perfect for everyday living.

Center this exquisite three-way glass table lamp among a seating group, or place it in a visible spot where its unique style and classic aesthetic will be noticed. A scalloped silhouette showcases soft blue hues with fading white overlay, bringing a romantic feel to its extraordinary artful look. A cream drum shade fashioned from stylish linen adds a perfect topping to a work of art designed to complement a modern or transitional space.
Features

Starting with a delicate glass construction, this elegant three-way table lamp becomes a source of rich color and top-tier décor. Dress up a main living space or bedroom with a classic blue glass lamp with a lovely silhouette, as flakes of gold dot its serene body. Designed by an Asian artist, this lamp is topped with a crisp white empire shade that makes it stand out.

Classic meets modern with this pink teardrop table lamp, accented with a stunning glimmery body that injects a hint of glam. This glass lamp incorporates all elements of beauty and modern decor, including a crystal base and a coordinating finial. The silk drum style shade ensures any space is spectacularly illuminated.

The elegance of tradition is seen in this trellis designed cut corner rectangle lamp which is highlighted by exquisite floral handles. The lamp is accented with a slopping cut corner oval shade featuring a braided gallery to put a finishing touch on the piece.

Myriad lily pad details create compelling texture and dimension for this decorative ceramic table lamp. In a natural green coloration, the lamp sits atop a round crystal base for an elevated touch on a side table or credenza. A beautiful white linen drum shade completes the look and ensures lovely, true illumination in any room.

Tall and grand, this slender contemporary glass table lamp is the sophisticated finishing touch you've been searching for. Its sleek glass body boasts a striking white lace design that captures attention and instantly elevates any tablescape. It sits on a crystal base and is topped with cream linen oval shade for soft, true illumination. Inspired by a classic Hollywood red carpet dress, the backside of the lamp has a plunging lace decor exposing the naked glass.

Bring a touch of the sea to your coastal decor with this exceptional coral table lamp. From Barclay Butera, the lamp boasts a gorgeous sculpted coral body resting atop a mahogany finish base. Rich in detail and character, the lamp is topped with a rectangular empire shade of sea grass that adds just the perfect touch of texture and natural elegance.
Medium white jar hand thrown ceramic with twin cobalt blue rope links to serve as a pull on the top
Three drawer navy and white side chest

attrib__switch_type: Four way switch on medium base socket. Switch one - off. Switch Two - both lights on. Switch Three - Medium base light on only. Switch Four - Candelabra base light on only.
